title: N Biren Singh: From Footballer, BSF Jawan & Journalist to Manipur CM for the 2nd Time - News18
content: N Biren Singh: From Footballer, BSF Jawan & Journalist to Manipur CM for the 2nd Time  News18View Full coverage on Google News
description: The Bharatiya Janata Party had contested the Manipur polls under the leadership of Biren, but he was still fighting for the top post as Biswajit Singh, another aspirant, had been in the BJP longer than the CM
